<p align="center"><em>Akasha means the basis and essence of all things in the material world; the first material element created from the astral world. </em></p>

<p align="center"><em>AkashaCMS is a suite of Node.js based tools with which you can convert ideas into websites while maintaining separation between content, layout and design.</em></p>

<p>This section of akashacms.com concerns the newly redesigned version of AkashaCMS.  The main portion of akashacms.com still documents the old AkashaCMS because the new documentation, that you're reading here, is a work in progress.  When browsing the repositories, the <tt>akasharender</tt> branch contains the new version.</p>

